（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bb57c4a9cf4c", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114060", "c": "131", "s": "0307", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "公共政策", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試警察人員考試、一般警察人員考試、國家安全情報人員考試、移民行政人員考試、退除役軍人轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "retired", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('retired-7fec267e-moex-00004', 'retired-7fec267e', 'retired-7fec267e-moex-114-adc7838e', 'sub-retired-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'essay', '賽蒙（H. Simon）認為在現實世界中，決策者是行政人（administrative
